---
Source:
  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  ID: 50ae0a98-5702-40cb-8c11-4c6297aa457a
  Translator: Burton Watson
By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 17
  Paragraph: 28
Title: Autumn Floods
---
The K'uei envies the millepede, the millepede envies the snake, the
snake envies the wind, the wind envies the eye, and the eye envies the
mind.
